        "description": {
            "chat": "",
            "unidentified": "",
            "value": "<p>Wings free you from the shackles of the ground below.</p>\n<p>Add the bat and bird forms in @Compendium[pf2e.spells-srd.Aerial Form]{Aerial Form} to your <em>wild shape</em> list.</p>\n<p>If you have @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.Insect Shape]{Insect Shape}, you also add the wasp form to your <em>wild shape</em> list. If you have @Compendium[pf2e.feats-srd.Ferocious Shape]{Ferocious Shape}, you also add the pterosaur form to your <em>wild shape</em> list.</p>\n<p>Whenever you use <em>wild shape</em> to gain a form that grants you a specific Acrobatics modifier, you gain a +1 status bonus to Acrobatics checks.</p>"
